    Difference between Two Groups (Non-parametric Tests for Independent and Paired Samples)

    np2groups(
  calculate = "selectpower",
  paired = FALSE,
  paired.r = 0.5,
  stdinput = FALSE,
  d = 0.2,
  mu1 = 0.2,
  mu2 = 0,
  sd1 = 1,
  sd2 = 1,
  margin = 0,
  power = 0.8,
  alpha = 0.05,
  alternative = "not equal",
  distribution = "normal",
  method = "normal",
  kappa = 1,
  n2 = 200
)
